    "The platform offers policy definition functionalities based on a proper form-based interface (Figure 5).",
    "A policy is defined in terms of the name and a description of the policy, the owner of the policy, and the purpose of the policy.",
    "It also allows end users to associate datasets to policies.",
    "Moreover, users can indicate key performance indicators (KPIs) for the policy.",
    "Following the definition of a policy, end users can also change some of its properties."
